Package: RcppSpdlog
Type: Package
Title: 'spdlog' C++ Header Library for Logging
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2020-08-18
Author: Dirk Eddelbuettel
Maintainer: Dirk Eddelbuettel <edd@debian.org>
Description: 'spdlog' is a mature and widely-used C++ library for logging with many
 desirable features that was written by Gabi Melman, and released under a MIT license.
 'spdlog' itself includes the 'fmt' library by Victor Zverovich which is also released
 under a MIT license. This package bundles these header files for easy use by R packages
 via a simple 'LinkingTo:' inclusion. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
